navigation, or more precisely, how to navigate in the file tree structure 
of your computer.


We need a couple of tools for making this work in a proper way.

stat

command

.bash_history





examples:
 man cp
 cp --help

 man apropos
 apropos --help

 gcc --help
 man gcc

